  "title": "Merchandising Associate | FMCG Manufacturing MNC | West",
  "description": "<p>Our client is a MNC in FMCG Manufacturing. Due to business needs, they are now recruiting a Merchandiser to be part of their Sales Team for ongoing transformation projects. They are located in the <strong>West - easily accessible.</strong></p><p><strong>Duties of Merchandiser:</strong></p><ul><li>Build and maintain strong relationships with both new and existing customers.</li><li>Monitor inventory levels, in-store displays, and competitor activities, and report updates to the Sales Executive.</li><li>Replenish and merchandise products to ensure neat, attractive, and well-organized displays.</li><li>Coordinate with store personnel to secure better shelf placement and additional display space.</li><li>Execute promotional activities and ensure timely setup of POSM materials.</li><li>Maintain stock hygiene and minimize out-of-stock situations.</li><li>Support sales performance while ensuring compliance with workplace safety and security standards.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Comfortable with islandwide travelling</li><li>Min 2 years of FMCG merchandising experience in handling multiple stores</li></ul><p>Interested candidates who wish to apply for the advertised position, please click <strong>APPLY NOW</strong> or email an updated copy of your resume/cv.</p><p>We regret that only shortlisted candidate will be notified.</p><ul><li><strong>Email Address: </strong><a href=\"mailto:jobs@recruitpedia.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>jobs@recruitpedia.sg</strong></a></li><li>EA License No: 19C9682</li><li>EA Personnel No: R2198636 (Oh Puey Xin)</li></ul>",
